  "info": {
    "title": "Aspose.PSD Resize CLI App for .NET",
    "version": "24.6.0",
    "description": "Aspose.PSD Resize CLI App for .NET provides resize functionality for PSD, PSB and AI file formats without requiring Adobe Photoshop or Adobe Illustrator. It supports resizing of the PSD and PSB files with a taking into account all the internal features of the format, including resizing of masks, shapes, smart layers, text layers. The result of resize operation can be exported to one of the supported formats including PSD, PSB, PNG, JPEG, PDF, TIFF, GIF, BMP, JPEG2000. PSD CLI Resize App supports quick and pixel-perfect (in the most cases) exporting of resized image. It can be used as standalone console application on the any platform that supports .NET including Windows, MacOS, MacOS-Arm, Linux. This App is frequently used for business process automation or CI/CD improving."
  },
